	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Colendissimo domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingero</persName> <persName ref="p8432" cert="high">Federicus a Salice</persName> S. D.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Paucis iam diebus elapsis scripsi tibi, colendissime domine <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Bullingere</persName>, neque nunc, quod illis adiiciam, habeo quicquam;, nos enim satis prospere valemus, suntque in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l648" cert="high">Rhaetia</placeName> nostra omnia in tuto dei beneficio.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nundinas <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l98" cert="high">Churienses</placeName> proxime praeteritas negociorum meorum turbine praepeditus non accessi; ex illis autem aliquid novi, quod et tibi significarem, operiebar, at nihil penitus intellexi eoque laetor; quo enim minus novarum rerum accipimus, eo melius habemus.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus deus foelicem hunc statum nostrum perpetuo dignetur prosperare.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De antichristi creatione nihildum certi audio, etsi adfuerint, qui asseverarunt cardinalem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1060" cert="high">Mantuanum</placeName> rerum summa potitum.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Veneti passim et per totum dominium suum praesidia auxere.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In ducatu <placeName ref="l306" cert="high">Mediolanensi</placeName>, ut referunt, circiter 3000 <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanorum</placeName> militum conscripta et hinc inde in hyberna divisa sunt.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid vero sibi haec externorum militum praeparatio velit, incertum est, et diversi diverse sentiunt; ego vero arbitror reliquias esse exercitus, qui iam aliquot annis in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l736" cert="high">Pedemonte</placeName> militarunt, qui cum hoc importuno ad sulcandum mare tempore in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispaniam</placeName> commodius traiici non possint, ut in officio permaneant, nec hinc et inde in subditos desaeviant, ita sint in hyberna divisi et vere proximo debeant in Hispaniam reduci.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De filio tuo <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p475" cert="high">Christophero</persName> nihil adhuc accepi, et iam pridem est, quod a Venetiis nullas omnino literas habui; si vero quid accipiam, confestim ad te transmittam.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Reliquum est, ut bene valeas cum tuis omnibus meque iugiter commendatum habeas.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale iterum atque iterum et foelicissime.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Filius meus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8433">Ioannes</persName>, qui ludum hic litterarium frequentat diligenter, se tibi commendat teque cum tota familia tua plurimum salvere iubet.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salutabis, quaeso, meo nomine plurimum etiam reverendos senes d. <persName ref="p8111" cert="high">Petrum Martirem</persName> et d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2336" cert="high">Bernardinum Occhinum</persName>, tuos generos omnes et d. consocerum tuum <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8011">Waltherum</persName>, viros utique multis nominibus insignes.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Iterum aeternum vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Datum <placeName ref="l96" cert="high">Clavennae</placeName> 27. novembris 1559.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8022" cert="high">Franciscus Niger</persName> ante paucos dies e <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l505">Tyrano</placeName> huc migravit tanquam in locum amoeniorem et salubriorem.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Illustris matrona <persName type="auto_name">Isabella</persName> utcunque bene habet, sed et d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2019" cert="high">Augustinus Maynardus</persName>, quantum prae ingravescente aetate licet, bene habet, omnesque te plurimum iubent salvere.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Idem qui supra tibi omnium deditissimus <persName ref="p8432" cert="high">Federicus a Salice</persName>, commissarius comitatus <placeName ref="l96" cert="high">Clavennensis</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ornatissimo et clarissimo viro domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Henrico Bullingero</persName>, domino meo iugiter colendissimo.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helvetiorum</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="de" type="auto">[Dem] hoch- und wolgelerten herren [mai]ster <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Hainrichen Bullingern</persName> zum Grossen Münster predicanten, minem insonderß gunstigen, lieben herren.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Zuͦ <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Zurich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
